data.description: Your Residence Awaits! Meticulously crafted in a gated community, this property offers an open concept, wood laminate floors, and modern bathrooms with a stylish barn door entrance to the master. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, an island with bonus storage. Smart home ready, wired for surround sound inside and out, providing seamless entertainment. Backyard features a covered patio, a dedicated dog run, and enchanting front and back jellyfish lighting, creating a captivating ambiance. Built by Lennar, this home combines quality craftsmanship with contemporary charm. Secure your tour today!
